<paragraph id="1711369DFF91FFC8D3D7FF10FE72FF43" blockId="16.[151,532,151,211]" box="[151,396,186,211]" pageId="16" pageNumber="117">
<figureCitation id="8F952A18FF91FFC8D3D7FF10FEE9FF43" box="[151,279,186,211]" captionStart="FIGURES 25 – 38" captionStartId="22.[151,264,1922,1945]" captionTargetBox="[256,1381,227,1921]" captionTargetId="figure@22.[201,1406,193,1932]" captionTargetPageId="22" captionText="FIGURES 25 – 38. Species of Hishimonus and Litura. 25 &amp; 26. H. phycitis (Distant) dark color morph; 27 &amp; 28. H. spicans sp. nov.; 29 &amp; 30. H. thapai sp. nov.; 31 – 33. H. viraktamathi Knight, color variation; 34 &amp; 35. H. zeylanicus sp. nov.; 36 &amp; 37. Litura unda Knight; 38. Litura triangula sp. nov. Figs 25, 27, 29, 31, 32, 34, 36, 38. Dorsal view; Figs 26, 28, 30, 33, 35, 37. Dorsolateral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/225639/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="117">
Figs 
<number id="A16624BAFF91FFC8D38EFF10FEE9FF43" box="[206,279,186,211]" pageId="16" pageNumber="117" value="17625.5" valueMax="35217.0" valueMin="34.0">34–35</number>
</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="8F952A18FF91FFC8D262FF11FE76FF43" box="[290,392,187,211]" captionStart="FIGURES 205 – 223" captionStartId="35.[151,264,1815,1838]" captionTargetBox="[242,1304,207,1774]" captionTargetId="figure@35.[208,1343,186,1796]" captionTargetPageId="35" captionText="FIGURES 205 – 223. Species of Hishimonus. 205 – 216. Hishimonus viraktamathi Knight.: 205. Head and thorax, dorsal view; 206. Head and thorax, profile; 207. Face; 208. Male pygofer, lateral view; 209. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 210. Style, dorsal view; 211. Connective, dorsal view; 212. Aedeagus lateral view; 213. Aedeagus, posterior view; 214. Female sternite VII, ventral view; 215. Second pair of valvula, lateral view; 216. Apex of second pair of valvulae, lateral view magnified. 217 – 224. Hishimonus zeylanicus sp. nov.: 217. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 218. Connective, dorsal view; 219. Style, dorsal view; 220. Apophysis of style, lateral view; 221. Aedeagus, posterior view; 222. Aedeagal shaft, lateral view. 223. Aedeagus, anterior view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/225652/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="117">
217– 
<number id="A16624BAFF91FFC8D21DFF11FE76FF43" box="[349,392,187,211]" pageId="16" pageNumber="117" value="223.0">223</number>
</figureCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1711369DFF91FFC8D3D7FEA8FD4BFEF3" blockId="16.[151,1436,258,967]" pageId="16" pageNumber="117">
Coloration as in 
<taxonomicName id="D0AE4D1EFF91FFC8D21FFEAEFE0FFE8B" box="[351,497,258,283]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Hishimonus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="distinctus">
<emphasis id="25DAEA8FFF91FFC8D21FFEAEFE0FFE8B" box="[351,497,258,283]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="117">H. distinctus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Paler specimens lack fascia on legs. Darker specimens with subapical spot on anterior surface of profemora and apical and basal spot on posterior surface, mid femora with two bands on subapical region and bases of setae, dark brown.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="5FB46516FF91FFC8D387FEC4FC46FD37" pageId="16" pageNumber="117" type="description">
<paragraph id="1711369DFF91FFC8D387FEC4FC36FD13" blockId="16.[151,1436,258,967]" pageId="16" pageNumber="117">
<emphasis id="25DAEA8FFF91FFC8D387FEC4FE93FE17" box="[199,365,366,391]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="117">
<collectingCountry id="6FB9760DFF91FFC8D387FEC4FEFFFE17" box="[199,257,366,391]" name="Malta" pageId="16" pageNumber="117">Male</collectingCountry>
genitalia
</emphasis>
. Pygofer in lateral view longer than its height, posterior margin broadly rounded, macrosetae confined to posterior submargin; valve with broadly rounded posterior margin. Subgenital plate with posterior fingerlike process 
<number id="A16624BAFF91FFC8D224FE1DFE6BFE5F" box="[356,405,439,463]" pageId="16" pageNumber="117" value="0.33">0.33</number>
times total length, lateral margin convex. Style 
<number id="A16624BAFF91FFC8D0EBFE1CFC30FE5F" box="[939,974,438,463]" pageId="16" pageNumber="117" value="2.5">2.5</number>
times as long as wide at base, with rather straight apophysis, subapical lobe well defined. Connective with stem shorter than arms. Aedeagus with basal processes arising almost on well developed dorsal apodeme, directed dorsally and remote from shaft in lateral view, 
<number id="A16624BAFF91FFC8D399FD89FEF4FDAB" box="[217,266,547,571]" pageId="16" pageNumber="117" value="0.33">0.33</number>
length of aedeagal shaft; each shaft divergent in basal half and then convergent, in posterior view, broad at base then tapered, inwardly curved in distal 
<number id="A16624BAFF91FFC8D1E2FDEDFD2DFDCF" box="[674,723,583,607]" pageId="16" pageNumber="117" value="0.33">0.33</number>
length; in lateral view shaft tapered and abruptly narrowed and filamentous beyond gonopore and directed dorsally; gonopore subapical.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1711369DFF91FFC8D387FD25FC46FD37" blockId="16.[151,1436,258,967]" box="[199,952,654,679]" pageId="16" pageNumber="117">
<emphasis id="25DAEA8FFF91FFC8D387FD25FE97FD36" box="[199,361,655,678]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="117">Measurements</emphasis>
. 
<collectingCountry id="6FB9760DFF91FFC8D237FD24FE4FFD37" box="[375,433,654,679]" name="Malta" pageId="16" pageNumber="117">Male</collectingCountry>
<quantity id="D0569B78FF91FFC8D2F8FD24FDE2FD36" box="[440,540,654,679]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" pageId="16" pageNumber="117" unit="mm" value="3.5">3.50 mm</quantity>
long and 
<quantity id="D0569B78FF91FFC8D1CAFD25FD10FD36" box="[650,750,655,679]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.2" pageId="16" pageNumber="117" unit="mm" value="1.2">1.20 mm</quantity>
wide across eyes.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
